<h2>About Movies</h2>
<p>Movies blend storytelling, visuals, sound, and performance into a unique art form.
From silent films to streaming blockbusters, the medium keeps evolving.</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Silent era → Talkies:</strong> 1890s–1930s</li>
  <li><strong>Studio Golden Age:</strong> 1930s–1950s</li>
  <li><strong>New Wave & Blockbusters:</strong> 1960s–1980s</li>
  <li><strong>Digital & Streaming:</strong> 1990s–Now</li>
</ul>
